replies.body:
Thanks for looking out for your fellow Summoner's! {{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}} 

I'd ask that you _**don't**_ post that link anywhere because we don't want someone else accidentally clicking on it! You did the right thing by contacting us in a ticket to be sure your account is protected, and it would be a good idea for your friend to do the same.

For reference, [**here's**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201751784-Emails-from-Riot-Games) a list of all the emails Riot will use to contact you, any others are prooooobably not from us! You can also check [**this guide**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201751664-Protecting-Your-Account) for other steps you can take to protect your account.
